## BNK-004: Transfer Money

**User Story:** As a customer, I want to transfer money so that I can pay bills and send funds.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
1. Transfer between own accounts is available
2. Transfer to other accounts is available
3. Transfer requires amount and recipient
4. Transfer confirmation is shown
5. Transfer limit is enforced

